commit.message:
Fixed toolbar colors in the terminal app

The toolbar color when using the terminal app is set to body-bg (white) in jupyter's terminal.less. That rule has higher specificity than the one in the theme's notebook.less file and so takes precedence, making the toolbar white.

Fixed toolbar colors in the terminal app

The toolbar color when using the terminal app is set to body-bg (white) in jupyter's terminal.less. That rule has higher specificity than the one in the theme's notebook.less file and so takes precedence, making the toolbar white.
